    14‚Üí
    15‚Üí- [#600](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/pull/600) [`3aee20a`](https://github.com/supermacro/neverthrow/commit/3aee20a1c429062d26f440fde32a3f26ef05533a) Thanks [@m-shaka](https://github.com/m-shaka)! - docs: updated README.md about `safeTry` and added @deprecated tag to safeUnwrap
    16‚Üí
    17‚Üí## 8.1.0
    18‚Üí
    19‚Üí### Minor Changes
